title: Diana's Classic Armenian Cuisine
typeOfFood: Mediterranean, Fast food, Take-out, Armenian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Traditional Armenian dishes with the usual vegetable items. Vegetarian platter includes hummus, baba ghanoush, yalanchi, and tabbouleh (ask for no pilaf). Other offerings include a falafel sandwich, dolma, and white bean salad. Please let HappyCow if there are vegan options and whether this place should remain listed.
